3, \"to\": 920}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 931}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that Pierre de Coubertin, IOC founder, revitalized the Olympic Games 130 years ago with the vision of using them to foster bridges and understanding among nations and peoples from around the world.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 995, \"end\": 1014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre de Coubertin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\"}, {\"begin\": 1016, \"end\": 1019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1174338334417787e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1058}, {\"ngram\": \"the vision\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1088}, {\"ngram\": \"bridges\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1120}, {\"ngram\": \"understanding\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1138}, {\"ngram\": \"nations\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"peoples\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1164}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Similarly, the Nishan Forum aligns with this vision by enhancing understanding between civilizations through dialogue and exchanges, drawing on the wisdom of Confucius to promote mutual respect and cultural exchange, Bach said.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1347, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour